2ffeaf980225b7b2c1f04665edeb3dac8d3a6c0d.query:
SELECT
                a.id,
                a.customer_id,
                a.value,
                c.name
            FROM
                customer_contact_channels a
                LEFT JOIN customers b ON b.id = a.customer_id
                LEFT JOIN contact_channels c ON c.id = a.contact_channel_id
            WHERE 
                a.customer_id = $1 AND b.merchant_id = $2 AND a.deleted_at IS NULL
            GROUP BY
                a.id, c.name

31f74893ede911745e109a3821eb3532a250215d.query:
SELECT 
                invoices.id, 
                invoices.invoice_number, 
                invoices.customer_id, 
                customers.name as customer_name, 
                invoices.total_amount, 
                invoices.invoice_date, 
                invoices.created_at, 
                job_schedules.id IS NOT NULL as is_scheduled,
                job_schedules.status = 'completed' as is_completed,
                invoices.title,
                invoices.description
            FROM invoices
                INNER JOIN customers ON customers.id = invoices.customer_id
                LEFT JOIN job_schedules ON job_schedules.job_data->>'invoice_id' = invoices.id::text
            WHERE invoices.merchant_id = $1
            ORDER BY invoices.created_at DESC

620d4ce418e7ca7f4a1316702cc989b808778328.query:
SELECT 
                invoices.id, 
                invoices.invoice_number, 
                invoices.customer_id, 
                customers.name as customer_name, 
                invoices.total_amount, 
                invoices.invoice_date, 
                invoices.created_at, 
                job_schedules.id IS NOT NULL as is_scheduled,
                job_schedules.status = 'completed' as is_completed,
                invoices.title,
                invoices.description 
            FROM invoices
                INNER JOIN merchants ON merchants.id = invoices.merchant_id
                INNER JOIN users ON users.id = merchants.user_id
                INNER JOIN customers ON customers.id = invoices.customer_id

            ORDER BY invoices.created_at DESC
